<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Project Title — Noran Morsi</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f8f1e8;
      --text: #2d211c;
      --muted: #7d675d;
      --line: #dfcdbb;
      --berry: #8f5873;
      --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: var(--transition); }

    /* Layout Structure */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Sidebar - Kept exactly the same for consistency */
    .sidebar {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .sidebar h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .sidebar p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
    
    .nav { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .nav a { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .nav a:hover { color: var(--berry); transform: translateX(4px); }

    /* Main Content Area */
    .main {
      padding: 4rem 3rem;
      max-width: 900px; /* Narrower for better reading */
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .back-link:hover { color: var(--berry); }

    .project-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .project-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    /* Project Content Styling */
    .project-content img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .project-content p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    /* Video/Embed Container */
    .video-container {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 ratio */
      height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #000;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sidebar { height: auto; position: relative; border-right: none; padding: 2rem; }
      .nav { flex-direction: row; gap: 1.5rem; }
      .main { padding: 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="brand">
        <a href="index.html"><h1>Noran Morsi</h1></a>
        <p>Visual Journalist</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="index.html">Work</a>
        <a href="index.html#about">About</a>
        <a href="index.html#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← Back to Projects</a>

      <article class="project-header">
        <h2>Project Title Goes Here</h2>
        
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span><strong>Client:</strong> New York Times (Example)</span>
          <span><strong>Role:</strong> Illustration & Research</span>
          <span><strong>Year:</strong> 2025</span>
        </div>

        <section class="project-content">
          <p>
            Start with a strong intro. Describe the "why" behind this project—the reporting 
            challenge, the cultural context, or the visual approach you took to bring this story to life.
          </p>

          <img src="images/placeholder-large.jpg" alt="Description of work">

          <h3>The Process</h3>
          <p>
            Talk about your techniques here. Whether it was on-the-ground reporting in Cairo or 
            data scraping in NYC, this is where you show your expertise as a journalist.
          </p>

          <p>
            Wrap up with the impact of the story or where it was published/broadcast.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

      <footer style="margin-top: 5rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line);">
        <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
          &copy; 2026 Noran Morsi. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
